     C                   exsr      pag01
     C                   eval      refrsh = *off
     C                   endif
     C     optnse        endsr
     *----------------------------------------------------------------
     *
     *  OPTNS2   Execute individual options
     *
     C     optns2        begsr
     C                   exsr      inzpar
     C                   eval      $puky = wkokyu
     *
     *   Change
