     C                   endif
     *
     *  INITIALIZE VARIABLES FOR LOOKUP
     *
     C                   eval      p = 0
     C                   eval      top = *off
     C                   eval      bot = *off
     C                   eval      stop = *off
     *
     *  READ SPECIFIED FLITCHES FILE
